room_title: Escape room "The Pharaoh's Tomb" by EXcape Columbus in Columbus
room_description: You and your team have been sent to Egypt to recover the stolen Emeralds in the tomb of King Tutankhamen. The ancient Pyramid is filled with secrets as you and your team explore with lanterns and flashlights. You must find the stolen gems and eXcape the tomb before the curse of the pharaohs begins in one hour.
